First off, I just want to say that I have no idea what I'm doing. It's really difficult to do research here on what's a bug, what's intended behavior, and when things changed. So, my apologies if this issue isn't actually a bug after all!

---

Repro steps:

`ConsoleApp1.csproj`:
```xml
<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">
